{"tid":1779401,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【母忘警暴】全港孤立唾棄黑警大行動","createTime":"2019-12-11T15:49:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T15:49:53.000Z","uid":120847,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"99763c97cd88934833967a1474e5695899f0973f","tid":1779401,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T15:49:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">經過今次運動，香港警察已經徹底腐化，演變成一個與民為敵，嗜血成性，視人命如草芥，視百姓皆螻蟻嘅恐怖集團</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">我地要令每一個警員都被社會摒棄同孤立。<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我要佢地被孤立，被拒絕，被斷交。<br />\n務求要佢地流血流汗嘅同時，要<span style=\"color: teal;\">流淚</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n作為社會一員，你有責任<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.做生意/開舖嘅你，今日起因行政同保安理由，拒絕服務警員，並張貼呢張平安符係門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可保生意興隆，貨如輪轉<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/LgZJF7p.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 打工嘅你，迫於無奈要為黑警提供服務時，可以調節一下服務態度質素同效率<br />\n<br />\n3. 有家人或者朋友做黑警嘅話，以最惡毒說話咀咒佢地，然後同佢立即斷絕來往，並鼓勵其他朋友一同孤立黑警<br />\n<br />\n4. 有小朋友/為人師表嘅你，向小朋友講解黑警嘅暴行，教導佢地明辨是非，並且提防黑警保護自己<br />\n<br />\n5. 一同向各國政府要求制裁香港警察<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yT7vAKm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyT7vAKm.png&h=b55eae31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XFrcO4n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXFrcO4n.png&h=f953b733&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n既然大家武力不對等，我地就無謂再送頭<br />\n我地以社會壓力將呢群禽獸孤立起黎<br />\n呢個係作為一個人應有嘅基本良知同底線<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地一定要讓仇恨延續下去，<br />\n直至黑警被清算，被唾棄，被毀滅。</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"879f1404dc5483c1f60c96b9fd8422322cece18d","tid":1779401,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T15:49:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}